Exception-    It is unexpected situation where Java is unable to proceed with the code.
            And the further flow of the program breaks down
Example-     1. Any value dividef by zero
             2. Accessing any value out of the range of an array
Exception handling- To do make the execution of a program uninterrupted, we should handle the Exception

Errors-     It indicate serious problems and abnormal conditions that most applications should not try to handle
            Error defines problem that are not expected to be caught under normal circumstances by our program.
            For Example memory error, computer error, JVM error etc. 
            